OL,3,CLife for woman who murdered husband
OL,4,Cafter birthday night out
OL,6,FA woman has been jailed for life for
OL,7,Fmurdering her husband after a birthday
OL,8,Fdrinking session in what the judge
OL,9,Fcalled a "senseless act of violence."
OL,11,FLisa Ellwood got into an argument with
OL,12,Fher husband Ryan Ellwood at their home
OL,13,Fin after downing cocktails on her
OL,14,Fbirthday night out.
OL,16,FEllwood, 40, had used her arm to hold
OL,17,FRyan against some kitchen cabinets and
OL,18,Fgrabbed a kitchen knife from a drawer
OL,19,Fbefore stabbing him once in the chest
OL,20,Fat their home on Greenwood Court on 29
OL,21,FAugust last year.
