OL,3,CLife for woman who murdered husband
OL,4,Cafter birthday night out
OL,6,FThe court heard that she had made a
OL,7,Fcomment about Ryan being ill and being
OL,8,F"too weak to fight" her off.
OL,10,FHe died after the knife pierced his
OL,11,Frib, lung and aorta.
OL,13,FEllwood claimed to have no
OL,14,Frecollection of the attack.
OL,16,FLeeds Crown Court heard Lisa Ellwood
OL,17,Fhad attacked Ryan in the past and
OL,18,Fthere was evidence they had been
OL,19,Fviolent to one another.
