OL,6,FThe court heard that Ryan's family,
OL,7,Fincluding his former wife, and their
OL,8,Ftwo children, had been left devastated
OL,9,Fby his death.
OL,11,FIn a victim statement, Ryan's sister
OL,12,FLucy described the last six months as
OL,13,Fa 'living hell' for the family and
OL,14,Fsaid his murder had caused "utter
OL,15,Fdevastation"
OL,17,FShe said: "Our lives will never be the
OL,18,Fsame again. We will never get over how
OL,19,FRyan was taken from us."
