OL,6,FThe court was told that Ellwood was
OL,7,Fdrinking a bottle of vodka every
OL,8,Fcouple of days and had been the victim
OL,9,Fof an abusive childhood.
OL,11,FRecorder of Leeds His Honour Judge Guy
OL,12,FKearl, sentencing Ellwood to a life,
OL,13,Fwith a minimum term of 16 years,
OL,14,Fdescribed the murder as a "senseless
OL,15,Fact of violence".
